{"tid":1907253,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印尼官員稱異性泳池同游會令女性懷孕　網民炮轟","createTime":"2020-03-02T13:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T13:35:05.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a05c02066daa6939434290c0f2003bf1832b2069","tid":1907253,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e58dffea5af56141f1d6a1b.jpg/rv18pcMqRJsMphZrN_C018k_FQC3nZqPBGHGmgRhxpo?v=w960r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e58dffea5af56141f1d6a1b.jpg%2Frv18pcMqRJsMphZrN_C018k_FQC3nZqPBGHGmgRhxpo%3Fv%3Dw960r16_9&h=4522055b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼一名保護兒童高級官員上周稱男女不應同池游泳，因如有男子在池中射精會令婦女有機會受孕。不少網民對於如此沒常識的言論大肆批評和嘲笑。<br />\n印尼媒體Tribun Jakarta報道，任職印尼兒童保護委員會的專員的西蒂（Sitti Hikmawatty）警告，如精子強壯的男子在水中射精，有可能導致池中女性懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://她在接受Tribunnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%A5%B9%E5%9C%A8%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97Tribunnews.com&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=c548d22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">她在接受Tribunnews.com</a>訪問談及青少年懷孕的議題是指出：「在泳池中有些精子是非常強壯的。如一個人（男子）的性慾被喚起並（在泳池）射精，可能會（導致女性）懷孕，即使（他們）沒有發生性行為。」<br />\n<br />\n印尼醫生協會（Indonesian Doctors Association，IDI）的會長納扎爾（Nazar）之後指出，女性不可能在泳池中受孕。她指出，泳池水有氯及其他化學物質，精子是不能在這些條件下生存。<br />\n<br />\n印尼一位有多達170萬追隨者的「醫生KOL」也發文回應。博客Blog Dokter寫道：「再次提醒你，如果你根本不了解健康問題，最好保持安靜。否則你的言論會導致焦慮與恐慌。」他說：「我在此強調，與異性一同游泳不會懷孕。不是所有在游泳的男人都會射精，以及精子是不能在有氯的泳池水中生存，更不要說游到（女性的 ）陰道了。」<br />\n<br />\n除了上述兩人，有些印尼網民亦批評西蒂的言論，指她應為有關言論辭職或是被炒。<br />\n<br />\n西蒂被專家及網民在網上「狂炸」之後，23日發聲明向公眾道歉，稱這是個人言論，以及她收回有關言論。政府已組成一個3人委員會，將決定是否對西蒂進行制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%8A%B1%E9%82%8A/440943/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1%E7%95%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E5%90%8C%E6%B8%B8%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A4%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%82%AE%E8%BD%9F?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25A3%2587%25E8%258A%25B1%25E9%2582%258A%2F440943%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2595%25B0%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25B3%25B3%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25AD%2595-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BD%259F%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BNqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=fd4c24a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%8A%B1%E9%82%8A/440943/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E7%A8%B1%E7%95%B0%E6%80%A7%E6%B3%B3%E6%B1%A0%E5%90%8C%E6%B8%B8%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A4%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%87%B7%E5%AD%95-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%82%AE%E8%BD%9F?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"69078a162caf36bb9127c0dfacacc80ee70dfd74","tid":1907253,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"喺泳池打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7edea8b97f0ca1c2ee2551e2b952a297f19282b","tid":1907253,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"笑唔出<br />\n我地香港咁繁榮都有議員叫人蒸口罩"},{"pid":"5d1d6e8a183f3046c00e0fa0f63297fa03d4af84","tid":1907253,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:12:13.000Z","msg":"又無講錯，游游下，<br />\n點知條賓周會插到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4525e6b83f708a724ebad6bc95abc61a67f6a2b8","tid":1907253,"uid":25420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:15:09.000Z","msg":"張相果個泳池<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d578963fa20929d815ec6f264cae37814b4241ab","tid":1907253,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:15:32.000Z","msg":"點解要呢個泳池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f296ccab30277c65e836bae1d61279c504ae14","tid":1907253,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhk01就咪鬼放上來"},{"pid":"df9637ecb106fbe8360d61ba8014822dc7b31c3a","tid":1907253,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"佢係咪大咗肚解釋唔到<br />\n所以要鳩噏掩飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}